Non-toxic Oil for Vacuum Pumps 220V ISO 46 Mineral White 5 Liters
Non-toxic oil specially formulated with bases and additives in the proper proportions to meet the requirements
of the food industry, standard H1, for lubricants in indirect contact with food. Designed for various
applications within the food and pharmaceutical industry.
